Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.88,0:00:02.85,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Doamnă profesoară...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.85,0:00:04.58,main,Rio,0,0,0,,You're getting married, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.71,0:00:11.11,main,Celia,0,0,0,,This wedding is something \NI have agreed to, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.68,0:00:14.86,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Even though the person \Nyou're marrying... is Charles Arbor?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:17.94,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Then, will you marry me instead, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.94,0:00:23.37,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Or will you take me somewhere and\Nlive the rest of your life with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.11,0:00:26.30,main,Charles,0,0,0,,Celia...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.71,0:00:29.99,italics,Celia,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.79,0:00:31.89,italics,Celia,0,0,0,,a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:36.09,main,soldier 1,0,0,0,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:38.68,main,soldier 2,0,0,0,,Seize him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:43.18,main,soldier 3,0,0,0,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:45.15,main,soldier,0,0,0,,Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:46.48,main,soldier,0,0,0,,Seize him! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:50.28,main,knight captain,0,0,0,,Fall back to the side and \Nform a single-file wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:52.19,main,knight captain,0,0,0,,Don't let him get close!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:00:59.62,main,knight captain,0,0,0,,Mage squad, contain him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.32,0:01:02.08,main,mages,0,0,0,,Photon Bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.09,0:01:13.92,main,knight captain,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:15.97,main,knight captain,0,0,0,,Protect the bride and groom!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:18.64,main,knights,0,0,0,,Enchant Physical Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:24.73,main,knight captain,0,0,0,,Encircle and capture him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:25.52,main,knights,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.18,0:01:28.65,main,Charles,0,0,0,,Everything is fine, Celia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:31.10,main,Charles,0,0,0,,This is just a nice show before the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.10,0:01:34.33,main,Charles,0,0,0,,They are the elite among \Nthe elite of our kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:38.56,main,Charles,0,0,0,,the chosen few with proven \Npedigrees and skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:47.66,main,Charles,0,0,0,,No lawless brigand could \Npossibly hope to topple...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:03.68,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Um...
