Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:40.78,main,Roland,0,0,0,,Celia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:43.16,main,Vanessa,0,0,0,,Count Claire, please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:45.34,main,Duke Arbor,0,0,0,,That fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.34,0:03:47.83,main,Duke Arbor,0,0,0,,Bringing disgrace upon my house...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:49.08,main,guard A,0,0,0,,Duke Arbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:51.16,main,Roland,0,0,0,,Unhand me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:54.00,main,Roland,0,0,0,,The security for this was \Nsupposed to be flawless!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:55.99,main,Vanessa,0,0,0,,We will do everything we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:59.09,main,Vanessa,0,0,0,,So, please, don't provoke the insurgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.73,0:04:00.76,main,Vanessa,0,0,0,,My lord Count!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:05.23,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Professor Celia...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:08.35,main,Rio,0,0,0,,I apologize for the disturbance,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:11.85,main,Rio,0,0,0,,but while those around us are in turmoil, \NI'd like to explain the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:15.15,main,Rio,0,0,0,,If you would keep quiet for a little \Nwhile, it would be a great help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:17.71,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio, what is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:21.85,main,Rio,0,0,0,,I am speaking directly into your \Nconsciousness through telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:27.58,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Focus your words in your mind\N and your voice will reach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:29.62,main,Charles,0,0,0,,Y-You villain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:31.25,main,Charles,0,0,0,,What do you want here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.26,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:35.05,main,Rio,0,0,0,,I have a grievance with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:38.78,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll just go ahead and \Ncrush your spine under my foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:41.78,main,Celia,0,0,0,,H-Hold on, Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:46.07,main,Rio,0,0,0,,I won't kill anyone. This is an act,\N part of the disturbance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:47.97,main,Celia,0,0,0,,A-All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:53.43,italics,Charles,0,0,0,,Why is he... so strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:57.94,main,Rio,0,0,0,,We don't have much time. \NI'll finish explaining quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:57.94,top,Alfred; background,0,0,0,,Take the guests into the inner sanctum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:05:02.23,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Before you are wed, I want to ask \Nonce more, what is your will?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:06.51,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Just for that, you've done all this...\N I told you already! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.89,main,Rio,0,0,0,,I said I want to know your will, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:14.96,main,Rio,0,0,0,,You're being half-threatened into this \Nby Duke Arbor's house, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.95,main,Duke Arbor,0,0,0,,What is the security team doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:24.84,main,Rio,0,0,0,,If you wish it, Professor, \NI will put an end to this wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:27.51,main,Celia,0,0,0,,You're being domineering!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:31.84,main,Rio,0,0,0,,I know full well that I'm being \Ndomineering and arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:35.23,main,Rio,0,0,0,,But, Professor, you are precious \Nto me. I owe you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:39.82,main,Rio,0,0,0,,I don't want to just dstand by \Nand lose what's important to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:42.75,main,Rio,0,0,0,,I know I'd regret it for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.98,0:05:55.07,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Once something is lost, \Nit will never come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:58.12,main,Rio,0,0,0,,but if you haven't lost it yet, \Nthen there's still time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:03.63,main,Rio,0,0,0,,I see a future where your dignity will \Nbe trampled on for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:05.68,main,Rio,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able stand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:10.15,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Professor, will this marriage make you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:17.18,main,Celia,0,0,0,,If I put my own feelings before all else,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:20.69,main,Celia,0,0,0,,I may cause trouble for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.89,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Would that... be the right thing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:26.68,main,Rio,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.64,0:06:31.61,main,Rio,0,0,0,,But if this wedding were \Ntruly the right thing to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:34.08,main,Rio,0,0,0,,then you wouldn't have that look on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:38.30,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Professor, I will make your wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:40.85,main,Rio,0,0,0,,So, please, don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:45.98,main,Celia,0,0,0,,If I say I don't want to get married, \Nwhat are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:49.68,main,Rio,0,0,0,,I will take you and run away from this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:53.85,main,Rio,0,0,0,,That way, no one would question whether \NCount Claire was involved, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:56.43,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Why would that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:01.81,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio, they'll catch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:07.03,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I will make your \Nwish come true, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:11.66,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Though that isn't something someone holding \Na knife to your throat should be saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:16.44,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:20.66,main,Celia,0,0,0,,I... want you to take me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:25.59,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:26.96,main,Rio,0,0,0,,I've decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:28.13,main,Rio,0,0,0,,I made up my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:29.34,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Feel the humiliation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:33.05,main,Rio,0,0,0,,I will abduct your bride \Nright before everyone's eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:37.68,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:43.06,main,Charles,0,0,0,,Celia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:46.00,main,Celia,0,0,0,,L-Lord Charles!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:47.73,main,Roland,0,0,0,,C-Celia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:50.85,italics,Celia,0,0,0,,I-I'm so sorry, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:53.70,italics,Celia,0,0,0,,I promise I'll see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:58.20,main,Charles,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Hurry up and capture him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:00.08,main,section commander,0,0,0,,All troops, after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:00.95,main,Alfred,0,0,0,,Hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:02.96,main,Alfred,0,0,0,,Do not break formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:05.71,main,Charles,0,0,0,,You lot, catch him immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:07.05,main,section commander,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:08.21,main,soldiers,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:09.21,main,Alfred,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:10.55,main,section commander,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:14.47,main,section commander,0,0,0,,H-Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:16.69,main,Charles,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.69,0:08:18.25,main,Charles,0,0,0,,Are you all incompetent?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:20.22,main,Alfred,0,0,0,,This was his intent from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:23.98,main,Alfred,0,0,0,,Didn't you see his jumping \Nability when he charged in?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:26.69,main,mages,0,0,0,,Photon Bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:32.95,italics,Reiss,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:36.89,italics,Reiss,0,0,0,,I thought he was using some kind \Nof magic item, but... spirit arts?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:39.87,italics,Reiss,0,0,0,,Could he have been the one back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:51.88,italics,Reiss,0,0,0,,He's gotten stronger since \Nthe last time I saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:54.93,italics,Reiss,0,0,0,,In that case, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:01.52,main,Charles,0,0,0,,Celia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:07.13,italics,Reiss,0,0,0,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:09.32,main,Charles,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:12.36,main,Charles,0,0,0,,Stop firing! What if you hit Celia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:16.87,main,Charles,0,0,0,,After him! Catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:18.04,main,Alfred,0,0,0,,Everyone, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:22.92,main,Alfred,0,0,0,,Our Aerial Knights are now in pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:27.71,main,Alfred,0,0,0,,All forces will now immediately spread \Nout in a net that encircles the capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:29.88,main,troops,0,0,0,,S-Sir! Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:34.18,main,Alfred,0,0,0,,And I will leave the security of \Nthese grounds to you, Vanessa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:37.25,main,Alfred,0,0,0,,Coordinate between the captains of each unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:38.93,main,Alfred,0,0,0,,Show me how well you keep things moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:41.90,main,Vanessa,0,0,0,,Sir! Understood, Elder Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.90,0:09:43.60,main,Charles,0,0,0,,Alfred!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:48.23,main,Charles,0,0,0,,You've let the raider get away. \NWho gave you permission to take command?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:53.19,main,Alfred,0,0,0,,More importantly, do you have any \Nidea who the insurgent might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:09:58.45,main,Charles,0,0,0,,He said he had a grievance with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:10:01.45,main,Alfred,0,0,0,,It sounds like there may be a lot of candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:03.18,main,Charles,0,0,0,,S-Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:05.20,main,Charles,0,0,0,,You go and chase him, too! Immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:06.81,main,Charles,0,0,0,,Catch him and bring him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:08.25,main,Alfred,0,0,0,,That is my intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:09.10,main,Alfred,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:12.76,main,Charles,0,0,0,,Blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:15.80,main,Charles,0,0,0,,Blast. Blast! Blast him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:19.58,italics,Reiss,0,0,0,,This has become quite an \Nentertaining situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:21.80,italics,Reiss,0,0,0,,but with the protections afforded \Nto me as an ambassador,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:24.81,italics,Reiss,0,0,0,,I suppose I shouldn't slip away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:31.71,italics,Reiss,0,0,0,,I am very interested in him, and that \Nspirit that never showed itself, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:40.24,main,Celia,0,0,0,,W-Wait, Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:43.62,main,Celia,0,0,0,,This is fast. We're going \Nvery fast, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:46.76,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Yes. Please be sure to hold on tightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:52.65,main,Rio,0,0,0,,I'd rather not deal with griffin unit, \Nso I'm going to go a little faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:55.00,main,Celia,0,0,0,,A-All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:11:00.09,main,Celia,0,0,0,,You've grown into quite an impressive boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:02.34,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:05.04,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Have you gotten a little \Nmore used to this speed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:08.35,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Yup! If you can go faster, bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:09.23,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:11.51,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Did you hear that just now, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:13.27,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Then I'll take you at your word.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:21.85,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Even if I keep running like this, \Nit will take time to shake them off,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:23.40,main,Rio,0,0,0,,so we'll head down for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:27.33,main,Rio,0,0,0,,I'll be passing on the baton, \Nso we'll meet up again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:33.17,main,Celia,0,0,0,,P-Passing on the baton? And what \Ndo you mean, "meet up later"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:35.01,main,Rio,0,0,0,,It's part of the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:37.17,main,Rio,0,0,0,,The truth is, I have someone helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:39.74,main,Rio,0,0,0,,The girl who first spoke \Nto you telepathically.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:50.70,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Aishia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:55.92,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Then, just as we planned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:57.46,main,Aishia,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:58.66,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:12:00.69,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Wait! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:04.19,main,Rio,0,0,0,,I'll play decoy and buy some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:09.07,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Professor, you and she will use this chance \Nto escape the royal capital together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:11.46,main,Rio,0,0,0,,I promise I will meet up with you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:14.10,main,Rio,0,0,0,,And to explain about this girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:16.21,main,Aishia,0,0,0,,I'll explain on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:17.99,main,Rio,0,0,0,,That's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.99,0:12:19.76,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Look after her for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:21.47,main,Celia,0,0,0,,W-Wait, Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:22.67,main,Celia,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.21,0:12:26.82,main,Aishia,0,0,0,,Shall we go, Celia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:28.51,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:33.52,main,aerial knight 1,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:36.86,main,aerial knight 2,0,0,0,,But I don't see Lady Celia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:39.85,main,aerial knight captain,0,0,0,,The alley he came out of is a dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:41.40,main,aerial knight captain,0,0,0,,Inform the teams on the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:42.40,main,aerial knight captain,0,0,0,,Send up a flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.26,main,aerial knight 1,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:45.82,main,aerial knight 1,0,0,0,,Signal Flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:52.29,italics,Rio,0,0,0,,They've called for reinforcements. \NIt's going just as we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:55.58,italics,Rio,0,0,0,,All that's left is for me to make \Na big show in drawing them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.91,0:12:57.58,main,aerial knights,0,0,0,,Blitz Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:10.85,main,aerial knight 2,0,0,0,,He's so quick at evading!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:12.76,main,aerial knight captain,0,0,0,,Continue the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:14.37,main,aerial knights,0,0,0,,Blitz Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:23.82,main,knight 7,0,0,0,,Over there! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:26.36,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Like I'd let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:50.05,italics,Rio,0,0,0,,There really are a lot of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:01.54,main,knight 7,0,0,0,,Don't give him a chance to rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:04.94,main,knight 7,0,0,0,,Reinforcements are coming. \NLet's wear him down as much as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:06.13,main,knights,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:09.87,italics,Rio,0,0,0,,Not killing anyone... \Nmight be making this tougher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:11.83,italics,Rio,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:15.50,italics,Rio,0,0,0,,I just told Professor Celia not to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:17.30,italics,Rio,0,0,0,,I can't give up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:18.79,main,Alfred,0,0,0,,That's as far as you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:21.00,main,Alfred,0,0,0,,I will now restrain you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:23.00,main,knights,0,0,0,,Lord Alfred!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:24.84,italics,Rio,0,0,0,,Alfred?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:27.55,italics,Rio,0,0,0,,He's the one they call the \NKing's Sword, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:33.53,main,Alfred,0,0,0,,You will only add to the number of injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:35.98,main,Alfred,0,0,0,,All of you, stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:36.85,main,knights,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:55.74,italics,Rio,0,0,0,,He's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:14.05,italics,Rio,0,0,0,,There's some kind of powerful \Nmagic formula cast on that sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:36.99,main,knight 7,0,0,0,,L-Lord Alfred is being pushed back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:51.34,main,Alfred,0,0,0,,Why do you not turn your blades on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.87,0:15:55.51,main,Alfred,0,0,0,,It seems you underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:57.65,main,Alfred,0,0,0,,But that ends now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:22.53,main,aerial knight captain,0,0,0,,Lord Alfred!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:26.25,main,aerial knight captain,0,0,0,,I don't see the insurgent anywhere.\N What happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:30.90,italics,Alfred,0,0,0,,If he took the full force of the blow, \Nnot a trace of him would be left, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:33.99,italics,Alfred,0,0,0,,I didn't feel it hit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:36.72,italics,Alfred,0,0,0,,And there's evidence he \Nfled into the back streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:39.22,main,Alfred,0,0,0,,Just to be sure, search the surrounding area!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.07,0:16:41.78,main,Alfred,0,0,0,,And we'll look for Miss Celia as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:42.56,main,knights,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:19.26,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Aishia... Rio is all right, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:22.77,main,Aishia,0,0,0,,He's fine. He's almost here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:31.23,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Aishia?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:33.15,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Is he really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:35.26,main,Rio,0,0,0,,I've just returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:44.87,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio! I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:52.65,main,Rio,0,0,0,,I know I worried you, but everything \Nis all right now, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:54.86,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:58.28,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio, you aren't hurt, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:17:59.42,main,Rio,0,0,0,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:00.47,main,Rio,0,0,0,,And Aishia...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:01.91,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:05.67,main,Aishia,0,0,0,,Not at all. I didn't do \Nanything of importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:08.10,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Well, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:09.47,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:13.15,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Is this really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:14.97,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Do you want to go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:17.71,main,Rio,0,0,0,,You could still make it in time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:19.99,main,Celia,0,0,0,,What? N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:26.00,main,Celia,0,0,0,,I was just thinking it doesn't \Nfeel real, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:31.96,main,Celia,0,0,0,,After all, for a moment my future was \Nso bleak, I thought my life was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:36.98,main,Celia,0,0,0,,But you're here with me now, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:40.97,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Thank you, Rio, for kidnapping me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:42.97,main,Rio,0,0,0,,You're very welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:47.69,main,Celia,0,0,0,,We'll have to think about \Nwhat we're going to do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:50.38,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Yes, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:55.48,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Professor Celia, I have something \NI absolutely must do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:19:01.96,main,Rio,0,0,0,,But I won't let you suffer for lack of \Nanything when it comes to daily necessities.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.96,0:19:03.49,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Rest assured on that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:06.62,main,Celia,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:10.43,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Well then, I suppose I'll take \Nyou up on that for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.16,0:19:14.42,main,Celia,0,0,0,,I am inexperienced and inept, \Nbut I hope you will look on me kindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:17.93,main,Rio,0,0,0,,I am the one who hopes you \Nwill look on me kindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,0:19:19.91,main,Celia,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:23.93,main,Celia,0,0,0,,Let's talk a lot to make up for all \Nthe time we didn't see each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:25.93,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Yes, let's!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:27.27,italics,Aishia,0,0,0,,It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:05.51,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Aishia?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:10.02,main,Aishia,0,0,0,,Haruto, please, help them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:10.90,main,Rio,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:13.52,main,Aishia,0,0,0,,I will protect Celia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:15.07,main,Aishia,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.26,0:21:52.33,main,Aki,0,0,0,,Masato, where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:53.54,main,Masato,0,0,0,,Don't ask me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:58.93,main,Miharu,0,0,0,,W-Well... for now, shall we \Ntry to find out where we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:02.55,sign_31638_280_No_Service,text,0,0,0,,Fără semnal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.99,0:22:01.23,main,Miharu,0,0,0,,Fără semnal?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:07.24,main,Masato,0,0,0,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:07.24,main,Aki,0,0,0,,Nu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:08.48,main,Miharu,0,0,0,,Masato!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.82,0:22:09.93,top,Aki,0,0,0,,Nu! Ajutor, cineva!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.48,0:22:09.93,top,Masato,0,0,0,,Aki-neechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.02,0:22:11.93,main,Miharu,0,0,0,,Please, don't do anything \Nhorrible with those children!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:15.06,top,man,0,0,0,,You go in a different cart. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.75,0:22:22.36,top,Rio,0,0,0,,One of your guards was carrying this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:24.96,top,man with hat,0,0,0,,What is that thing? \NDon't know anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.31,0:22:27.36,main,Aki,0,0,0,,Someone, help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.36,0:22:28.53,italics,Rio,0,0,0,,Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:31.62,main,Aki,0,0,0,,Please! Let us out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.82,0:22:45.51,main,Rio,0,0,0,,Is it just the two of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.34,0:22:48.67,main,Aki,0,0,0,,You speak Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:50.68,main,Masato,0,0,0,,There's one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.87,0:23:06.94,flashback,Haruto; 7 yo,0,0,0,,That way we can always be \Ntogether, side by side...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:09.61,flashback,Haruto; 7 yo,0,0,0,,Even if I die, I'll protect you, Mii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.28,0:23:12.49,flashback,Haruto; 7 yo,0,0,0,,Or, do you not want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.38,0:23:14.93,main,Rio,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.93,0:23:18.97,main,Miharu,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you so much for saving us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.42,0:23:22.50,main,Miharu,0,0,0,,My name is Ayase Miharu.
